Package: easieRnmt
Title: EasyNMT for R
Version: 0.0.1.0010
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Thiele", , "daniel.thiele@fu-berlin.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R wrapper around the EasyNMT python library, providing "Easy to use, state-of-the-art Neural Machine Translation for 100+ languages" locally.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
